th century.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 0aHaskalah. 0aJewish philosophy. 4aJewish Studies. 4aReligion -- Judaism. 7aRELIGION / Judaism / History.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804767682zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804767682423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804767682/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles